<h3>2. Data Usage</h3>
<p>Your data is used solely to enhance your experience with StoreManagement. We do not share or sell your personal information to third parties unless required by law.</p>

<h3>3. Data Protection</h3>
<p>We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access. Your data is stored securely, and we maintain confidentiality in accordance with applicable privacy laws.</p>

<h3>4. Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at <strong>support@storemanagement.com</strong>.</p>
